ik zu skizzieren.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aArchitecture and DesignxArchitecturexUrbanism. 4aArchitekturgeschichte. 7aARCHITECTURE / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertBWF Online Paketz9783035603347oZDB-23-BBF08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Architecture, Design and Arts 2000 - 2014z9783110635690oZDB-23-GAA0 cprintz978376436497740uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978303560267840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783035602678423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783035602678/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_AD  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-BBF  aZDB-23-GAAc2000d2014